	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Songs fizzle if you aren't skilled in the particular instrument type of the song you are trying to sing (even if you aren't trying to use an instrument).&nbsp;&nbsp;For example, if you haven't trained up your brass skill by using a brass instrument, Denon's Disruptive Dischord will fizzle about 80% of the time.<br><br>The easiest way to train up these skills is to grab the appropriate instrument, find a quiet corner and just set your character to sing one song.<br><br>Hope that helps.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
